  description="See how CoderClaw compares to GitHub Copilot, Cursor, and Claude. CoderClaw is the only framework built for autonomous agents, sub-agents, and full mesh orchestration."
  canonicalUrl="https://coderclaw.ai/docs/coderclaw-vs-alternatives"
